data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience at this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home in the coveted Frenship ISD! Go Tigers!     This immaculate home boasts an open floor plan with plenty of space for everyone. The recently installed can lighting compliments the freshly painted interior, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.     Relax in style, and let this home be your retreat from the world. The isolated primary suite boasts a separate shower and soaker tub, with a large walk-in horseshoe closet. The updated kitchen showcases luxurious quartz countertops, tons of storage, sink with a window view and a roomy corner pantry. Finally, escape to the backyard donning gorgeous landscaping, hot tub, private TV book, large storage shed and plenty of room to run.    ALL of this in close proximity to Texas Tech, LCU, and the bustling medical district. Experience a blend of comfort, convenience, and accessibility, at a great price! Come see your next home today!
